visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: display
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Metal Mania

designer: Open Window

approved: true
description: <p>Metal Mania was inspired by lots \
  of Heavy Metal album covers and posters. Only \
  the most 'Metal' elements were combined to make \
  the quintessential Heavy Metal font. Looks good \
  on concert posters and guitar picks! Long live \
  Metal Mania.</p> \
  <p>First drawn were the inline forms and then they \
  were traced, utilizing a playful 'cutout' effect.</p> \
  <p>Designed by Dathan Boardman of Open Window.</p>

font.MetalMania-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.MetalMania-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

